gomodel:SYNGO_2247  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: PTPRF was enriched in postsynaptic density fractions.\n\n15/01/2018 Pim\n- Supplementary Fig. 1: \"The percentage of LAR clusters that colocalized with PSD-95 clusters was 54.1 ± 4.8% (DIV21) and 21.2 ± 2.4% (DIV7); the percentage that colocalized with bassoon was 52.8 ± 4.3%\" ... \"The immunocytochemical data and biochemical findings are consistent with LAR-RPTP being enriched at excitatory synapses but more widely distributed in neurons than PSD-95.\"\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Figure legend\nFigure 1: Expression pattern and fractionation of LAR-RPTP proteins in rat brain." , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5518-6584" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6194-9648" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_2247" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

